platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: In this highly enjoyable mixture of strategy and tactical action, you fortify your island base with real-world weaponry, manage your economy and amass armies to storm enemies beaches and seize their resources. To succeed in destroying other players strongholds, youll need to think strategically and make smart decisions on the fly. Boom Beach offers polished, compelling gameplay enhanced by excellent sound, an amusing visual style, and easy-to-use controls.
